<div id="Overview" class="blurbSummary grid_12">
  <div class="p">
    Conveyor is a technology that dramatically reduces the implementation and
    management overhead of operations management. At a high level, the idea
    and benefits are very similar to Ford's assembly line: increase worker
    productivity by encoding institutional knowledge in automated components
    leading to decreased cost, increased quality, and not incidentally,
    improved working conditions and compensation.
  </div>
</div>
